# ConTrackr — Construction Materials Delivery & Inventory Monitoring System
**CENG 116 – Database Management in Construction**  
**CavSU BSCE 4-2 | Group 2**

---

## System Overview

ConTrackr is a full-stack web application that manages:
- **Material Requests** — Auto-checks warehouse inventory, auto-stocks-out if available, auto-creates Purchase Request if insufficient stock
- **Procurement Workflow** — Purchase Requests (PR) → Canvass/Quotation → Purchase Orders (PO)
- **Delivery Tracking** — Record deliveries, confirm to auto-update inventory
- **Inventory Monitoring** — Real-time stock tracking per warehouse and per project site, low-stock alerts
- **Inter-Project Transfers** — Transfer materials between project sites or from warehouse with approval workflow
- **Reports & Analytics** — Transaction logs, inventory summary, stock movement charts

