## Troubleshooting

**MySQL connection error:**
- Make sure XAMPP MySQL is running (green in Control Panel)
- Check `.env` file has correct DB_PASSWORD

**npm not found:**
- Install Node.js from https://nodejs.org and restart Command Prompt

**Port already in use:**
- Backend (5000): Check if another app uses port 5000, change `PORT=5001` in `.env`
- Frontend (5173): Vite will automatically try the next port

**phpMyAdmin import fails:**
- Make sure you created `contrackr_db` first before importing
- Check that MySQL is running in XAMPP

